tsl:PolicyOrLegalNotice.tsl:TSLLegalNotice: The applicable legal framework for the present TSL implementation of the Trusted List of supervised/accredited Certification Service Providers for Spain is the Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures and its implementation in Spanish laws.
